{"tid":310891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【哈佛研究】一個月射精至少21次 患前列腺癌風險大減","createTime":"2017-07-06T07:25:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T09:24:50.000Z","uid":78546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"16817695ec908aa9bf928699745942807162379c","tid":310891,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:25:18.000Z","msg":"美國哈佛大學一項橫跨18年、涉及逾3萬人的研究顯示，男士每月射精至少21次可大幅減低患前列腺癌的風險。<br />\n<br />\n研究人員在1992年向31,925名年齡介乎20至29、40至49歲的男士派發問卷，了解他們的射精頻密程度，無論是經自慰或性行為的射精都計算在內，並追蹤他們直到2010年為止。研究期間3,839位男士確診前列腺癌。<br />\n<br />\n研究人員發現，相比每月射精4至7次的男士，每月射精至少21次的男士患前列腺癌的風險低得多。研究人員表示：「我們發現相比起報告射精較少的男士，射精較多的男士後來確診前列腺癌的可能性較低。」<br />\n<br />\n不過研究並無解兩者之間的原因，但哈佛大學過往有研究顯示，射精有助清除致癌物質的腺體，並或有助紓緩引致癌症的炎症。研究結果刊登於《歐洲泌尿》期刊<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170706&amp;guid=56920006&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170706%26guid%3D56920006%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&d=wVCdQDQd6V8kLTA4Gx1tzYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=f0ecf3e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170706%26guid%3D56920006%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&h=84e84668\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170706&amp;guid=56920006&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"b36fe19e4293284645d6eff7332f4f8d7582696b","tid":310891,"uid":50655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:27:14.000Z","msg":"手淫強身"},{"pid":"7ab4094fa209fc0b606264913fd6022c70efca4e","tid":310891,"uid":123712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:31:59.000Z","msg":"一滴精 十滴血"},{"pid":"430e21a5dfe36b0730a7c72f877b19b361d4ebbd","tid":310891,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:45:41.000Z","msg":"射咁多，傷身甩髮"},{"pid":"a285ca4edd3f1707b62b46b2215b7ee352ca59f6","tid":310891,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:54:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一滴精 十滴血</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁射幾多次精 = 捐一次血？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84ee6cd53d177afc711061f4bbd4c8737e315e8d","tid":310891,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:20:03.000Z","msg":"但腳軟風險大增"},{"pid":"3bd4c22abc87b2857f7ff2e2cf0d140641b8bfe2","tid":310891,"uid":70840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:23:14.000Z","msg":"一日一次腳軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n渣ga"},{"pid":"a62399f1c7a1395f6a67874c6c738e393722afaa","tid":310891,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:24:50.000Z","msg":"睇到戒J post果班人嘅未來"}]}